on|last=Bajkowski|date=15 April 2014|work=Manchester Evening News|publisher=MEN Media}}</ref>\n\nPlayers currently playing in the Premier League are highlighted in '''bold'''.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|+Most goals (career) \n|-\n! style=\"width:20px\" abbr=\"Position\"|Rank\n! style=\"width:175px\" |Name\n! style=\"width:40px\" abbr=\"Goals\"|Goals\n! style=\"width:40px\" abbr=\"Games Played\"|Games\n! style=\"width:65px\" abbr=\"Drawn\"|Goals per game\n! style=\"width:50px\" abbr=\"Position\"|Playing position\n! style=\"width:60px\" abbr=\"Season\"|First goal\n! style=\"width:60px\" abbr=\"Season\"|Last goal\n|-\n| 1\n|style=\"text-align:left\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Alan Shearer]] || '''260''' || 441 || 0.59 || [[Forward (association football)|Forward]] || [[1992\u201393 Premier League|1992\u201393]] || [[2005\u201306 Premier League|2005\u201306]] \n|-\n| 2\n|style=\"text-align:left\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Wayne Rooney]] || '''208''' || 491 || 0.42 || Forward || [[2002\u201303 Premier League|2002\u201303]] || [[2017\u201318 Premier League|2017\u201318]]\n|-\n| 3\n|style=\"text-align:left\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Andy Cole]] || '''187''' || 414 || 0.45 || Forward || [[1993\u201394 Premier League|1993\u201394]] || [[2006\u201307 Premier League|2006\u201307]]\n|-\n| 4\n|style=\"text-align:left\"| {{flagicon|ARG}} '''[[Sergio Ag\u00fcero]]'''|| '''180''' || 261 || 0.69 || Forward || [[2011\u201312 Premier League|2011\u201312]] || [[2019\u201320 Premier League|2019\u201320]]\n|-\n| 5\n|style=\"text-align:left\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Frank Lampard]] || '''177''' || 609 || 0.29 || [[Midfielder]] || [[1997\u201398 Premier League|1997\u201398]] || [[2014\u201315 Premier League|2014\u201315]]\n|-\n| 6\n|style=\"text-align:left\"| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Thierry Henry]] || '''175''' || 258 || 0.68 || Forward || [[1999\u20132000 Premier League|1999\u20132000]] || [[2011\u201312 Premier League|2011\u201312]]\n|-\n| 7\n|style=\"text-align:left\"| {{flagi